    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Nicknames indicating a diminutive or affectionate reference. In English, often made with the addition of a "y" or "ie."  An example would be "Annie" used for "Ann."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
